Reasoning: The paper analyzes the evolution of discussions on Wikipedia articles, which involves natural language processing and social network analysis. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Additionally, the paper also involves computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and possibly cybernetics (cs.CY) and systems and control (cs.SD) due to the analysis of complex systems and patterns of collective participation.
